1
00:00:07,300 --> 00:00:14,900
♪I look at you, like at another me♪

2
00:00:16,780 --> 00:00:24,540
♪My heart is locked up, never free♪

3
00:00:25,260 --> 00:00:34,420
♪Sometimes I go with it, spinning like a top♪

4
00:00:35,060 --> 00:00:44,300
♪No one to tell my secrets to, so I stay silent♪

5
00:00:47,700 --> 00:00:54,620
♪Loud is the echo I buried deep♪

6
00:00:57,300 --> 00:01:03,700
♪How I crave a single reply♪

7
00:01:04,060 --> 00:01:08,660
♪Lonely souls are sand in the wind♪

8
00:01:09,260 --> 00:01:13,620
♪With nowhere to settle♪

9
00:01:13,980 --> 00:01:18,460
♪Broken all over, yet my heart won't give♪

10
00:01:19,020 --> 00:01:24,220
♪Like a flower blooming in a crack of stone♪

11
00:01:24,420 --> 00:01:28,980
[Loving Strangers]

12
00:01:29,020 --> 00:01:33,940
[Episode 17]

13
00:02:05,870 --> 00:02:11,060
[Zhou Yu'an, Sen'an Pharma
Anything happen at home?]

14
00:02:14,750 --> 00:02:15,290
Sir,

15
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:17,220
I found a wallet by the sofa.

16
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,220
It has the owner's contact info inside.

17
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,170
Okay. Thanks.

18
00:02:25,580 --> 00:02:27,700
[Jiang Jiaqi, Director of Pharmacovigilance]

19
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:35,380
[Jiang Jiaqi, Director of PV Dept: Anything happen at home?]

20
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,850
I'm so sick of takeout.

21
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,340
I don't care what we eat.

22
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,540
We've been sitting all morning,

23
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,540
so let's go stretch a bit.

24
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:48,060
[Zhou Yu'an, Sen'an Pharma
Anything happen at home?]

25
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:53,730
You guys go ahead.

26
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,170
I'll catch up in a bit.

27
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,130
Hello?

28
00:02:58,190 --> 00:02:58,850
Hi.

29
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,130
Is this Mr. Jiang?

30
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,500
I'm the owner of the congee shop.

31
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,410
You left your wallet here.

32
00:03:03,430 --> 00:03:04,540
So it's with you.

33
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,340
Can I pick it up after work?

34
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,410
Sure.

35
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:08,220
I'll be here.

36
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,060
Thank you.

37
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:09,890
No problem.

38
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,980
Nothing wrong at home, right?

39
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:19,540
No.

40
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,540
You feeling okay?

41
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,060
I just slept in.

42
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,220
What are you doing?

43
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:36,100
How many orders did you take this morning?

44
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:37,100
Let me see.

45
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:37,890
Quit that!

46
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:39,200
You already took six.

47
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,410
You're all hyped up, huh?

48
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,060
More orders, more money.

49
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:42,890
More orders?

50
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:43,540
More money?

51
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,660
Your uncle here is only human.

52
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:47,290
And it's about time we ate!

53
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,290
You go ahead. I'm not hungry.

54
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:49,730
Jiang Jialu!

55
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,660
Jiang Jialu!

56
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:52,730
You've got something you can't shake.

57
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:54,200
So you're trying to distract yourself.

58
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,100
I get that.

59
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:56,850
But don't drag me into it!

60
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,290
What can't I shake off?

61
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,100
Right.

62
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:01,610
No, nothing at all.

63
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,450
Why is this coffee stain

64
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:10,450
so stubborn?

65
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,570
We can't wipe it off.

66
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,220
I've got stuff on my mind too.

67
00:04:16,170 --> 00:04:18,250
But I'm an honest guy.

68
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:19,560
If something's up,

69
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,900
I'll deal with it.

70
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,780
I'm an actor.

71
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:38,170
But when I see the camera,

72
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:39,250
I freak out.

73
00:04:39,950 --> 00:04:41,020
Forget being the lead,

74
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,580
I can't even play a small part.

75
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,140
Director,

76
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:47,900
I really can't go back.

77
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:50,490
Please turn me back.

78
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:08,780
You little punk.

79
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,900
Leave the delivery at the door.

80
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,370
Didn't I tell you?

81
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:40,490
Leave it at the door...

82
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:43,580
Director Jiang?

83
00:05:44,310 --> 00:05:45,700
I'll turn you back.

84
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,140
What did you say?

85
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:49,930
I said,

86
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:52,380
I'll turn you back into Ai Youyou like before.

87
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:53,700
I'll take responsibility for you.

88
00:05:55,630 --> 00:05:56,050
This...

89
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,410
this sounds like

90
00:05:57,950 --> 00:05:59,140
a soap opera line.

91
00:05:59,190 --> 00:06:00,050
What's wrong?

92
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:04,020
Do you remember

93
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:06,580
when you did my show back then,

94
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,700
you ad-libbed a line?

95
00:06:09,070 --> 00:06:10,370
The one about the blank sheet.

96
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:13,810
"I'm a blank sheet,

97
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,900
crumpled by you,

98
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:16,810
folded and torn,

99
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:18,980
rolled into a ball,

100
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,930
and tossed into the trash."

101
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:21,700
Right.

102
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,290
That one.

103
00:06:25,190 --> 00:06:26,170
You said

104
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,340
it was too cheesy.

105
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,850
Now I don't think so.

106
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,140
Back then you knew nothing,

107
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,700
so you were a blank sheet.

108
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,780
It was because you shot my film

109
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:35,810
that you got crumpled.

110
00:06:37,190 --> 00:06:37,660
So...

111
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:40,050
from now on,

112
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:42,780
I'll take responsibility for you,

113
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:45,460
until I smooth you out again.

114
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:48,780
Really?

115
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:50,170
Really.

116
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:53,810
So,

117
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,700
from now on, whenever you need me,

118
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:56,980
I'll be there on call.

119
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,460
Then you'd better keep your word.

120
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:06,170
I need you right now.

121
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:09,220
Can you give me a hug?

122
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:19,660
Well...

123
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:20,700
I still have work to do.

124
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,170
I'm going.

125
00:07:35,300 --> 00:07:37,560
[Sen'an Pharma]

126
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,410
Not appropriate.

127
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:40,610
Why not?

128
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,700
Jiang Jiaqi graduated

129
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:44,660
and came straight to Sen'an.

130
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,810
He worked in R&D for twelve years.

131
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,050
Since moving to Pharmacovigilance,

132
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,580
he's been diligent and responsible.

133
00:07:51,310 --> 00:07:52,170
In the past three years,

134
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,460
his performance reviews

135
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,340
among all the directors

136
00:07:54,390 --> 00:07:55,370
were always No. 1 or No. 2.

137
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,100
What year is this?

138
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,370
Still talking about seniority?

139
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:00,020
Ability is what matters.

140
00:08:00,430 --> 00:08:01,370
But not long ago,

141
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,700
he was investigated by the Inspection Office.

142
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,700
I heard someone might have bribed him.

143
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:05,540
Yeah.

144
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,100
Yeah what?

145
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:10,170
That whole thing

146
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,980
was already cleared by the Inspection Office.

147
00:08:13,310 --> 00:08:14,610
But the gifts were real.

148
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:16,580
No smoke without fire.

149
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:17,930
The Vice GM seat

150
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:18,810
comes with temptations

151
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:20,050
way more than usual.

152
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:20,930
As for this matter,

153
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,850
the Chairman has made his judgment.

154
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,140
So why are you

155
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:24,980
bringing it up again?

156
00:08:25,430 --> 00:08:26,540
Then let me ask this.

157
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,350
Jiang Jiaqi was doing great

158
00:08:28,350 --> 00:08:29,190
in R&D,

159
00:08:29,190 --> 00:08:30,140
so why on earth

160
00:08:30,190 --> 00:08:31,780
was he moved to PV?

161
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,290
What was HR thinking

162
00:08:33,290 --> 00:08:35,010
when you decided that?

163
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,460
Honestly, I suspect

164
00:08:36,550 --> 00:08:37,610
some people

165
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:39,130
just don't want Jiang Jiaqi to move up.

166
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,580
I don't like that.

167
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:42,100
At the national level,

168
00:08:42,150 --> 00:08:43,700
drug safety is getting more attention.

169
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:45,130
So PV, of course, needs someone

170
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,220
with an R&D background

171
00:08:46,220 --> 00:08:47,300
to take on the big work.

172
00:08:47,550 --> 00:08:48,960
As the Vice GM over HR,

173
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,670
it was clearly

174
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:50,770
because I value Jiang Jiaqi

175
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:52,300
that I sent him to PV.

176
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:53,130
So you're saying

177
00:08:53,550 --> 00:08:54,340
you do recognize

178
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,420
Jiang Jiaqi's ability,

179
00:08:55,550 --> 00:08:55,940
right?

180
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:02,300
Aren't there four candidates total?

181
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:03,610
If it's controversial,

182
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,650
why not just vote?

183
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:06,530
Sure.

184
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:08,980
More democracy from now on

185
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,010
isn't a bad thing.

186
00:09:10,910 --> 00:09:13,010
This time Jiang Jiaqi was nominated.

187
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:14,850
Yes, on paper, I recommended him,

188
00:09:14,910 --> 00:09:15,890
but it also represents

189
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,650
what the other shareholders want.

190
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:18,730
Meaning,

191
00:09:19,270 --> 00:09:20,530
we should pick talent without prejudice,

192
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,650
not bury the newcomers,

193
00:09:22,750 --> 00:09:24,580
and not chill the veterans.

194
00:09:25,510 --> 00:09:26,940
Everyone will have a chance

195
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,300
to shine for Sen'an

196
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,060
and do their part.

197
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,700
Alright, let's vote by a show of hands.

198
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,650
All in favor

199
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,580
of PV Director Jiang Jiaqi

200
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,060
as a Vice GM candidate,

201
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,220
please raise your hand.

202
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:49,700
[Notice: List of Approved Vice GM Candidates]

203
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:51,100
[R&D: Deng Ning, HR: Qiao Yunshan]

204
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:52,300
[Pharmacovigilance: Jiang Jiaqi]

205
00:09:53,390 --> 00:09:53,770
Boss.

206
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:54,890
Boss...

207
00:09:55,510 --> 00:09:56,010
Boss!

208
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,010
Quick, take a look!

209
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,300
The candidate list is out!

210
00:09:58,910 --> 00:09:59,250
Look.

211
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:01,610
PV, Jiang Jiaqi!

212
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:02,130
Yeah!

213
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:03,650
Congrats, Boss!

214
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:05,460
Congrats, Boss!

215
00:10:05,460 --> 00:10:06,250
You guys, take a look

216
00:10:06,270 --> 00:10:06,750
at that notice!

217
00:10:06,750 --> 00:10:07,890
Hurry! Take a look!

218
00:10:08,550 --> 00:10:09,100
Boss!

219
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,370
Congrats!

220
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:11,220
Congrats, Boss!

221
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:12,770
- Uh... - Congrats!

222
00:10:13,030 --> 00:10:14,350
What drinks do you want?

223
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:15,370
Post it in the group.

224
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:17,010
PV's buying!

225
00:10:17,050 --> 00:10:17,510
It's on us!

226
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:18,610
Okay!

227
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:19,420
Okay!

228
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:23,890
Congrats, Boss!

229
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:24,890
Congrats!

230
00:10:25,790 --> 00:10:26,610
Congrats, Director Jiang!

231
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:46,250
I figured they might

232
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,490
call for a vote,

233
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,730
so I already gave them

234
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:50,650
a heads-up.

235
00:10:51,510 --> 00:10:52,490
I just didn't expect them

236
00:10:52,790 --> 00:10:53,770
to flip that fast.

237
00:10:54,030 --> 00:10:55,650
Didn't you hear what Wang Licheng said?

238
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:57,020
He made it clear:

239
00:10:57,020 --> 00:10:58,600
If you want to shine at Sen'an,

240
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,610
it's not just through us;

241
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:00,980
you can follow him, too.

242
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:05,220
Good thing it's two to one right now.

243
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:08,370
I'll work on them,

244
00:11:08,750 --> 00:11:10,490
get the two sides to vote for Deng Ning,

245
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:11,820
and lock it down.

246
00:11:11,870 --> 00:11:13,580
You still dare say "lock it down"?

247
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,180
I remember, in this very room,

248
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,250
someone guaranteed me

249
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:19,130
Jiang Jiaqi wouldn't be nominated,

250
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:20,770
and wouldn't pass the screening,

251
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:21,460
and wouldn't become a candidate.

252
00:11:21,630 --> 00:11:22,370
But look now.

253
00:11:23,270 --> 00:11:24,420
Why did it end up like this?

254
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:26,460
I'm sorry, Mr. Gu.

255
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:27,250
"I'm sorry" won't help.

256
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:28,010
So what do we do?

257
00:11:29,550 --> 00:11:30,650
I'll do whatever it takes

258
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:31,770
to dig up dirt on him.

259
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:34,250
Then I'm counting on you.

260
00:11:48,220 --> 00:11:48,940
[Come out and meet me]

261
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:51,980
Congrats.

262
00:11:54,030 --> 00:11:54,980
Too early, don't you think?

263
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:56,530
Yeah.

264
00:11:57,550 --> 00:11:58,490
This is just the first round,

265
00:11:58,550 --> 00:11:59,420
the easiest one.

266
00:12:00,510 --> 00:12:01,610
Once you get the chance,

267
00:12:02,270 --> 00:12:04,060
step on it without hesitation

268
00:12:04,420 --> 00:12:05,770
and finish him for good.

269
00:12:10,010 --> 00:12:10,520
Hello?

270
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,130
You listening?

271
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,370
If you let him win

272
00:12:16,390 --> 00:12:17,490
because you're soft,

273
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,100
I won't forgive you.

274
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,700
Don't you dare disappoint me.

275
00:12:39,300 --> 00:12:42,340
[Sen'an Pharma]

276
00:12:57,550 --> 00:12:58,300
What about the photo

277
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,180
of you kissing Jiang Jiaqi?

278
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,180
Why is there zero buzz?

279
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,650
Luo Lingling already exposed it,

280
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,180
saying I seduced my boss.

281
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:10,530
Can you even tell

282
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,530
if you seduced him from the photo?

283
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,010
I found the moment

284
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,370
and tiptoed up to kiss him.

285
00:13:15,030 --> 00:13:15,670
Otherwise what?

286
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:16,890
You think he'd kiss me first?

287
00:13:17,550 --> 00:13:18,640
In the photo, who's making the move

288
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:19,530
is obvious.

289
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:20,800
Because of this,

290
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:22,010
I almost got fired by him.

