341
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:17,890
But you just slowly

342
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:20,180
keep this going.

343
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:22,420
I have a feeling

344
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:26,420
Jiang Jiaqi will really fall for you.

