384
00:19:55,300 --> 00:19:57,180
♪When the barriers between us are gone...♪

385
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:57,770
Congrats.

386
00:19:58,310 --> 00:19:59,140
You're getting promoted.

387
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:05,460
