388
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:09,730
Gu Chen won't just sit back.

389
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:11,860
He'll fight to stop me.

390
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:14,380
Make chances

391
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:15,620
