395
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:23,770
Of course it does.

396
00:20:24,480 --> 00:20:25,810
Who keeps having meals

397
00:20:25,920 --> 00:20:26,460
with someone

398
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:27,380
they don't like?

399
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:29,420
But people also eat together when they need something.

400
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:30,660
But Jiang Jiaqi

401
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:31,700
isn't that kind of guy.

402
00:20:32,310 --> 00:20:33,770
If he eats out

403
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:34,490
with you,

404
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:36,570
then he likes you.

405
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:41,940
You'll get it.

406
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:46,380
That sure?

407
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:50,420
And then make him leave

408
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:51,700
with his tail between his legs.

409
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:54,180
Why do you hate him so much?

410
00:20:56,270 --> 00:20:57,180
You barely even know him,

411
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,090
do you?

412
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:02,220
Because you hate him,

413
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:05,490
I hate him too.

414
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:10,580
♪Once again, we believe in clear skies♪

