521
00:25:07,750 --> 00:25:08,810
What's the matter?

522
00:25:11,030 --> 00:25:12,010
The notice came through.

523
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:13,620
We got you a bed.

524
00:25:17,830 --> 00:25:19,090
I heard this place is good,

525
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:22,010
with dedicated caregivers too.

526
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:23,530
And it's free.

527
00:25:24,790 --> 00:25:26,770
That's a good thing.

528
00:25:27,590 --> 00:25:31,090
Is it really free?

529
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:39,490
Don't worry. It doesn't cost a thing.

530
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:41,460
I'll make more money

531
00:25:41,550 --> 00:25:42,490
and pay back what I owe.

532
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:43,940
Once I've saved enough,

533
00:25:44,270 --> 00:25:45,490
we'll move to a better house,

534
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:47,220
and I'll care for you myself.

535
00:25:49,110 --> 00:25:52,730
I'm happy anywhere,

536
00:25:53,750 --> 00:25:54,940
as long as you can

537
00:25:55,070 --> 00:25:58,090
be done with him for good.

538
00:26:03,790 --> 00:26:05,530
I'm sorry.

539
00:26:13,510 --> 00:26:15,570
How did you find

540
00:26:16,510 --> 00:26:19,010
