543
00:26:26,590 --> 00:26:30,180
He's a really good person.

544
00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:33,380
You know,

545
00:26:34,270 --> 00:26:35,810
I haven't done much for my sister.

546
00:26:36,830 --> 00:26:38,090
And at my age,

547
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:40,530
