580
00:28:16,110 --> 00:28:16,490
Mom.

581
00:28:16,830 --> 00:28:17,250
Yijun,

582
00:28:17,590 --> 00:28:18,050
it's me.

583
00:28:18,510 --> 00:28:19,420
