584
00:28:20,270 --> 00:28:21,290
I just got home from work.

585
00:28:23,790 --> 00:28:24,010
So...

586
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:24,660
here's the thing.

587
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:25,860
This weekend,

588
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,140
if you have time,

589
00:28:27,350 --> 00:28:28,490
I'll buy some groceries.

590
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:29,940
Let's properly celebrate

591
00:28:30,030 --> 00:28:30,860
for Jiaqi,

592
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:31,980
give him a boost.

593
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:33,900
Celebrate what?

594
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:35,980
Jiaqi got promoted!

595
00:28:37,240 --> 00:28:38,530
I'm getting forgetful.

596
00:28:39,310 --> 00:28:40,940
He went out with Dongshan and Jialu.

597
00:28:41,070 --> 00:28:42,490
You haven't seen him today, right?

598
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:44,490
Mom, it's okay.

599
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:47,250
Anyway, if something makes him happy,

600
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:49,860
he'd share it with you first.

601
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,530
I should thank you.

602
00:28:54,070 --> 00:28:55,620
All the neighbors know

603
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:56,530
our family

604
00:28:56,550 --> 00:28:57,570
has a wonderful daughter-in-law.

605
00:28:58,270 --> 00:28:58,940
All these years,

606
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:00,090
you've held this family up

607
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:01,290
inside and out.

608
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:02,660
You've worked so hard.

609
00:29:03,380 --> 00:29:04,290
Mom, please stop.

610
00:29:04,300 --> 00:29:05,380
I'm not that great.

611
00:29:05,790 --> 00:29:06,380
It's true!

612
00:29:06,750 --> 00:29:08,490
Seeing you do better and better,

613
00:29:08,550 --> 00:29:09,940
it makes me truly happy!

614
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:15,640
Mom, I'm going to shower.

615
00:29:15,670 --> 00:29:16,420
We'll talk later.

616
00:29:17,790 --> 00:29:18,620
Go on.

617
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:19,980
No staying up late, okay?

618
00:29:26,900 --> 00:29:30,000
[Jiaqi]

619
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:31,900
I'm buying Mom some things.

620
00:29:32,480 --> 00:29:33,250
I'll be back a bit later.

621
00:29:38,590 --> 00:29:39,490
Even through the phone,

622
00:29:40,070 --> 00:29:40,980
I could tell

623
00:29:41,270 --> 00:29:42,530
my sister was smiling.

624
00:29:45,550 --> 00:29:46,490
If I don't get picked,

625
00:29:46,590 --> 00:29:47,490
you'll go explain it to her.

626
00:29:48,140 --> 00:29:49,050
Hey! Don't jinx it!

627
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:51,380
Jiaqi, you have to get it.

628
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:54,490
You know what I'm seeing?

629
00:29:58,720 --> 00:29:59,420
Some day,

630
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:02,490
right in the lobby of a five-star hotel,

631
00:30:03,750 --> 00:30:04,490
there is

632
00:30:04,590 --> 00:30:05,860
a giant peach cake this big.

633
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:08,900
With the guests all seated,

634
00:30:09,510 --> 00:30:10,700
every wrinkle on my sister's face

635
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:11,940
is smiling.

636
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:13,700
Today

637
00:30:13,790 --> 00:30:16,010
is the joyful 70th birthday

638
00:30:16,270 --> 00:30:19,010
of Ms. Yao Yumin!

639
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:21,570
Thank you!

640
00:30:22,960 --> 00:30:24,940
Before we invite the birthday lady onstage,

641
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:27,380
please allow me to grandly introduce

642
00:30:27,510 --> 00:30:30,350
the organizers of this magnificent banquet.

643
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:33,200
They are Ms. Yao Yumin's

644
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:34,630
outstanding eldest son,

645
00:30:34,830 --> 00:30:36,290
Sen'an Pharma Vice GM,

646
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:37,490
Jiang Jiaqi!

647
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:43,010
Her equally outstanding second son,

648
00:30:43,240 --> 00:30:44,290
the well-known director,

649
00:30:44,510 --> 00:30:45,330
Jiang Jialu!

650
00:30:47,110 --> 00:30:49,660
And Ms. Yao Yumin's

651
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:51,010
younger brother,

652
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:52,700
Yao Dongshan!

653
00:30:59,030 --> 00:31:00,620
Their devotion

654
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:02,380
truly moves us all.

655
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:03,810
Let's give another round of applause

656
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:04,940
to these three!

657
00:31:05,110 --> 00:31:07,420
- Great! - Great!

658
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:16,330
Isn't she that actress?

659
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:25,250
Why are you here?

660
00:31:25,880 --> 00:31:26,460
I was passing by.

661
00:31:27,030 --> 00:31:27,620
I thought

662
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:28,660
you were at Galaxy Tavern.

663
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:29,660
Didn't expect to run into you

664
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:30,420
the second I got here.

665
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:32,980
Uh, next time,

666
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:33,730
if you need me,

667
00:31:33,790 --> 00:31:34,860
just call me first.

668
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:37,860
Hi, Mr. Jiang.

669
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:39,220
Hello.

670
00:31:41,510 --> 00:31:42,220
And this is...?

671
00:31:43,110 --> 00:31:43,770
My brother.

672
00:31:45,160 --> 00:31:46,620
Wow, he really does look like you.

673
00:31:47,110 --> 00:31:47,940
Listen to you.

674
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:50,010
Same mom. Of course they look alike.

675
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:52,940
Well, enjoy your time.

676
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:53,810
I'm heading back.

677
00:31:57,270 --> 00:31:58,250
You guys have a good time.

678
00:31:58,310 --> 00:31:58,940
I should go too.

679
00:31:59,200 --> 00:31:59,620
Bye-bye.

680
00:31:59,880 --> 00:32:00,290
Bye-bye.

681
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:23,180
How are things going on your end?

682
00:32:24,070 --> 00:32:25,330
I told you all night.

683
00:32:25,720 --> 00:32:26,490
I'm just a candidate.

684
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,660
Is that what I'm asking?

685
00:32:30,070 --> 00:32:31,090
I'm asking about that girl.

686
00:32:31,720 --> 00:32:32,860
Have you been in touch lately?

687
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:35,570
Yeah.

688
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:38,250
What?

689
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:39,810
You're still in touch with her?

690
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:41,660
What for?

691
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:45,320
Drinking.

692
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:46,800
Talking.

693
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:48,140
If you want to drink and talk,

694
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:49,010
come find me.

695
00:32:49,270 --> 00:32:50,220
She's just a young girl.

696
00:32:50,220 --> 00:32:51,090
What would she know?

697
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:53,220
I don't know.

698
00:32:55,350 --> 00:32:56,050
But it feels like

699
00:32:56,070 --> 00:32:57,090
I've known her forever.

700
00:32:57,550 --> 00:32:57,980
Alright.

701
00:32:58,110 --> 00:32:58,980
Get home already.

702
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:00,700
I'm taking the route by the school.

703
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:02,700
It's dark on that path. Take care.

704
00:33:15,790 --> 00:33:16,940
Not coming up for a drink?

705
00:33:17,270 --> 00:33:17,660
No.

706
00:33:18,350 --> 00:33:19,290
I have to get up early tomorrow.

707
00:33:21,030 --> 00:33:21,530
Here for something?

708
00:33:22,310 --> 00:33:23,570
I'm here to tell you something.

709
00:33:23,750 --> 00:33:24,570
The director

710
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:25,490
I mentioned last time

711
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:27,050
wants me to audition again.

712
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:28,050
Really?

713
00:33:28,590 --> 00:33:29,660
Why all of a sudden?

714
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:31,080
They said

715
00:33:31,160 --> 00:33:32,180
they switched my role,

716
00:33:32,270 --> 00:33:33,730
which fits me better.

717
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:34,810
And...

718
00:33:35,270 --> 00:33:36,530
I was honest with the director too.

719
00:33:37,110 --> 00:33:38,730
I told him I freeze sometimes,

720
00:33:39,310 --> 00:33:40,860
and I get a bit stuck in my head.

721
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:43,050
He said this is a good chance

722
00:33:43,050 --> 00:33:44,490
to push through and toughen up.

723
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:46,140
That's great.

724
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:50,620
Thank you for what you said this morning,

725
00:33:51,350 --> 00:33:52,980
and... the hug.

726
00:33:56,750 --> 00:33:57,530
Well...

727
00:33:58,310 --> 00:33:59,290
is there anything else

728
00:33:59,400 --> 00:34:00,250
you need me to help with?

729
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:01,660
No.

730
00:34:03,350 --> 00:34:04,330
If I need you,

731
00:34:04,550 --> 00:34:05,290
I'll call you.

732
00:34:44,630 --> 00:34:45,300
I'm heading home.

733
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:46,300
Bye.

734
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,340
Do well tomorrow!

735
00:35:01,630 --> 00:35:02,570
Say it again.

736
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:09,900
Do well tomorrow.

737
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:16,570
Thank you.

738
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,170
That me you crumpled up

739
00:35:19,590 --> 00:35:20,860
has smoothed out a little now.

740
00:35:22,150 --> 00:35:22,650
Bye.

741
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:24,340
Bye.

742
00:35:30,150 --> 00:35:30,900
Good luck tomorrow!

743
00:35:34,110 --> 00:35:34,690
You too!

744
00:35:42,030 --> 00:35:42,900
Just that much?

745
00:35:48,780 --> 00:35:50,700
[Call log: Jiaqi]

746
00:35:53,060 --> 00:35:56,860
[Yijun]

747
00:35:58,230 --> 00:35:58,610
Hello?

748
00:35:59,670 --> 00:36:00,170
Hello.

749
00:36:02,510 --> 00:36:03,820
Are you on your way back?

750
00:36:04,670 --> 00:36:05,340
Yeah, I'm on the way.

751
00:36:06,630 --> 00:36:07,420
You called me earlier.

752
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:08,170
I missed it.

753
00:36:08,880 --> 00:36:09,740
What's up?

754
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:11,900
I was at the supermarket.

755
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:12,900
I just wanted to ask

756
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:13,900
if you needed anything.

757
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:17,050
No.

758
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:19,420
Is there something else

759
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:20,170
you want to tell me?

760
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:23,940
No.

761
00:36:25,300 --> 00:36:31,940
♪Loud is the echo I buried deep♪

762
00:36:35,140 --> 00:36:41,740
♪How I crave a single reply♪

763
00:36:42,020 --> 00:36:46,700
♪Lonely souls are sand in the wind♪

764
00:36:46,900 --> 00:36:51,460
♪With nowhere to settle♪

765
00:36:51,780 --> 00:36:56,540
♪Broken all over, yet my heart won't give♪

766
00:36:56,660 --> 00:37:06,660
♪Like a flower blooming in a crack of stone♪

767
00:37:20,860 --> 00:37:22,300
[Loving Strangers]

768
00:37:23,230 --> 00:37:23,860
Hello?

769
00:37:24,280 --> 00:37:25,260
Jiang Jiaqi, right?

770
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:26,170
Does your company

771
00:37:26,190 --> 00:37:27,130
have someone

772
00:37:27,360 --> 00:37:28,210
named Zhou Yu'an?

773
00:37:29,070 --> 00:37:30,380
What are you planning to do next?

774
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:31,420
A scandal?

775
00:37:31,590 --> 00:37:32,170
With whom?

776
00:37:32,480 --> 00:37:32,900
Me.

777
00:37:36,060 --> 00:37:43,100
♪Meeting flowers of barren lands...♪

778
00:37:43,110 --> 00:37:43,860
You're Chen Ren?

779
00:38:05,260 --> 00:38:08,660
♪A light hiding in the dark♪

780
00:38:09,340 --> 00:38:12,220
♪Reflects my panic inside♪

781
00:38:12,980 --> 00:38:17,300
♪Locked for so long in a narrow crack♪

782
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:22,740
♪Life chasing us into surrender♪

783
00:38:23,420 --> 00:38:26,740
♪We're all the same♪

784
00:38:27,140 --> 00:38:31,060
♪Burdened with a load that steals our breath♪

785
00:38:32,180 --> 00:38:37,420
♪Unwilling to live so ordinary♪

786
00:38:38,060 --> 00:38:41,300
♪But how do we even cry out♪

787
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:45,180
♪Our helplessness to the sky?♪

788
00:38:46,500 --> 00:38:49,580
♪When dandelions drift far away♪

789
00:38:49,860 --> 00:38:53,140
♪Lone buds fly against the wind♪

790
00:38:53,420 --> 00:38:56,740
♪Fleeing into a boundless haze♪

791
00:38:57,180 --> 00:39:00,300
♪Burying yesterday♪

792
00:39:00,500 --> 00:39:03,980
♪When dandelions drift far away♪

793
00:39:04,420 --> 00:39:07,540
♪Lone buds fly against the wind♪

794
00:39:07,980 --> 00:39:11,140
♪Fleeing into a boundless haze♪

795
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:14,460
♪Burying yesterday♪

796
00:39:14,940 --> 00:39:18,020
♪When dandelions sail far away♪

797
00:39:18,420 --> 00:39:21,500
♪Pushing me back to my first dream♪

798
00:39:21,900 --> 00:39:24,180
♪Even covered in scars♪

799
00:39:24,780 --> 00:39:27,740
♪I still press on♪
